            <title>2.1.18</title>
            <pubDate>Mon, 02 Mar 2026 11:15:02 -0500</pubDate>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>15.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[
                <h2>What's New</h2>
                <ul>
                <li>This update fixes a download/install problem that could make macOS block SaneBar after some unzip methods. It also improves icon moving and click behavior in Browse Icons and the second menu bar.</li>
                </ul>
                ]]>
            </description>
