<item>
            <title>2.1.16</title>
            <pubDate>Sat, 28 Feb 2026 21:36:28 -0500</pubDate>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>15.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[
                <h2>What's New</h2>
                <ul>
                <li>Improved auto-hide reliability when closing Icon Panel and switching browse views.</li>
                <li>Made icon movement refresh faster and more consistent across Hidden, Visible, and Always Hidden tabs.</li>
                <li>Improved launch stability to avoid duplicate-instance and permission confusion during testing and daily use.</li>
                </ul>
                ]]>
            </description>
